=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"&#x1f449;\"> Tối Ưu Tốc Độ WordPress trên VPS với Cache Disk &#8211; RAM<br>Trình bày: Mr. Minh Nguyễn | CEO Minh Duy Solutions</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"&#x1f449;\"> Tối Ưu Điểm Google Pagespeed Insight (Dự kiến)<br>Trình bày: Mr. Quyền Lê | CEO Bignet Solutions</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>Thời gian:</strong><br>09h00 &#8211; 11h30 ngày 06/06/2020 (GMT +7)</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"><strong> Địa điểm:</strong><br>TOONG coworking space Nha Trang (Dự kiến)<br>Số 1 Trần Hưng Đạo, Lộc Thọ, Thành phố Nha Trang</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>Đăng ký tham dự:</strong><br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FVnzCdMfjnQNknb1R8%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1JnwDgxhquL1EehsksX3ynE8hB_ADWcRz4wt89dhqH_vB4UkTubNbS6xo&amp;h=AT1uncA47tvtL51iemZh4bzPyXTNjLzYM4M5PZKOpUwY1eTovkfG03DEkf9n3_A2i5pZqS6Wh4YGCO-KGy8hOOgHxSwa_8tMB_i0v-jUSDX10mi92Fq4DVHDTG0veIDJL96h_Q9n-KuP3daMEDYR13Qdeg\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/VnzCdMfjnQNknb1R8</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>Các kênh truyền thông khác:</strong><br>&#8211; WordPress.Org:<br><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2020/05/24/nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-06-2020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://vi.wordpress.org/2020/05/24/nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-06-2020</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvi.wordpress.org%2F2020%2F05%2F24%2Fnha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-06-2020%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR27MNanH-fAebmdu8OomxYFpOXF3FqoHOlEiVFAD0GMPHoi5cdtKqx1KL4&amp;h=AT3Dwt88CHTuZCf5_f7ptXWpZ8Xl8OCsWXXkj0RspvhoDBibpcZ4RnTR_dkZ1oWJ-m18rFWV4tMCT0-0ujmQnKmtGa4oeMsEr5GHC2U17hjzE9pntG6hEnuhRoxEOSDOmK_mD0qKbkAW0TQ-K_yMqex90A\" target=\"_blank\">/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8211; Meetup.com:<br><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Nha-Trang-WordPress/events/270829975/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://www.meetup.com/Nha-Trang-WordPress/events/270829975/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"><strong> Quà tặng:</strong><br>&#8211; Hosting Miễn Phí của Minh Duy Solutions<br>&#8211; Dịch Vụ Tối Ưu Website của Bignet Solutions</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>Cám ơn đơn vị tài trợ địa điểm:</strong><br>Xin trân trọng cám ơn <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/toonggoldcoast/\">TOONG coworking space</a> đã nhiệt tình tài trợ địa điểm meetup cho Nha Trang WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>FAQ:</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"&#x1f449;\"> Nha Trang WordPress Meetup là hoạt động offline hàng tháng nhằm phát triển cộng đồng yêu thích và sử dụng WordPress tại Nha Trang<br><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"&#x1f449;\"> Nha Trang WordPress Meetup là LOCAL GROUP chính